      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PSIONIC PROWESS (1) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from seven starts. Below best last time at Capalaba (20.13) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fifth. Looks suited here and rates on top. SUMMER'S SCRUB (3) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey having won five of six starts. Was out of placings last time (20.58) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 12 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. REGAL SAINT (5) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (19.07) at Q Straight. Form here at this distance is sound. Expecting another good run. SING MY SONG (8) placed last time (21.85) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 4.5 lengths. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.",
